respStmt.resp: Transcription and correction of the printed edition

availability.p: This text is available for purposes of academic research and teaching only. Re-distribution in any form without prior permission is prohibited. Short extracts may be cited with full acknowledgement of the source.

series.title: Samlingar utgivna av Svenska fornskriftsällskapet. Serie 1: Svenska skrifter

projectDesc.p: This text has been encoded according to the Phrases and Clauses Tagging Manual for syntactic analyses of Old Nordic texts encoded as Menotic XML documents (PaCMan), version 2.0, at $$$.

correction.p: This text was proofread by the editor and co-workers. It is unlikely that it contains any significant number of errors.

normalization.p: This text follows the printed edition.

interpretation.p: The text has partly been analysed morphologically and syntactically.
